                     <list>
                        <item xml:id="a1">                          
                           <desc>Marginalia</desc> The work contains some Amharic marginalia; the
                           concluding leaves <locus from="260" to="267"> ff. 260-267</locus> contain
                           sales contracts and property listings, written in Amharic, of members of
                           Ethiopian nobility, dated roughly to <date notBefore="1750" notAfter="1780">1750-1780</date>.</item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <desc>Marginalia</desc> After the colophon on f.<locus from="173v" to="173v">173v</locus> some quotations from a comentator have been
                           added.</item>
                        
                     </list>
                  </additions>
